                    )
                div
                div(class="flex items-center justify-between")
                    a.text-gray-500.text-sm(href="/auth/registro") 多No tienes cuenta? Crea una
                    a.text-gray-500.text-sm(href="/auth/olvide-password") Olvide mi contrase単a
                input(
                    type="submit"
                    value="Iniciar sesion"
                    class="w-full py-2 border bg-indigo-500 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white uppercase font-bold transition-colors rounded-md md:cursor-pointer"
                )